{"_id":"post-523698b7-4bdc-4abb-8c84-c1b7826b322b","_type":"post","title":"Repl.it GFX: Native graphics development in the browser","slug":{"_type":"slug","current":"gfx"},"body":[{"_key":"b9210e06b838","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"At Repl.it we live and breathe making software creation easier. With our ","_key":"b9210e06b8380"},{"_type":"span","marks":["ef54b28831ae"],"text":"programming environment","_key":"b9210e06b8381"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", you could start coding in your favorite language in seconds. With ","_key":"b9210e06b8382"},{"_type":"span","marks":["1a99b8906659"],"text":"live deployments","_key":"b9210e06b8383"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", we made web hosting a breeze. With ","_key":"b9210e06b8384"},{"_type":"span","marks":["8ebe8d0974ff"],"text":"Multiplayer","_key":"b9210e06b8385"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":", we've removed the drudgery from coding with friends. And today, we're excited to bring native GUI applications and game development to the browser.","_key":"b9210e06b8386"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"ef54b28831ae","_type":"link","href":"platform"},{"_key":"1a99b8906659","_type":"link","href":"deploy"},{"_key":"8ebe8d0974ff","_type":"link","href":"multi"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"cda6d87a374d","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"cda6d87a374d0","text":"","marks":[]}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"6b2e34e748c1","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Before we go on, you have to see this in action: Just run the repl below, wait a few seconds for it to load, focus on the output window and start playing Tetris in Pygame:","_key":"6b2e34e748c10"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_type":"embed","_id":"21592892-7fb3-4954-a217-f4e832c507e4","url":"https://repl.it/@demcrepl/Tetris-in-Pygame?lite=true","_key":"d0d6c464696d"},{"_key":"b7e33e035751","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Let's take it up a notch and boot up this nifty desktop app we all love (might take up to a minute to load but then can be done recursively):","_key":"b7e33e0357510"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_type":"embed","_id":"ff6cde56-cb38-4a63-8136-e62a24ff4d80","url":"https://repl.it/@amasad/chrome?lite=true&outputonly=1","_key":"5ae36ff7d2e7"},{"_key":"57f878f7627e","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Why","_key":"57f878f7627e0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"10894f9fefe5","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We believe in the plurality and diversity of developer communities. That's why we spend countless days, weeks, and months working on features that can work cross language. We want programmers from all backgrounds, regardless of their language, to be able to code games and apps with ease. Plus, supporting native graphics opens us up to a wealth of frameworks, games, and educational material! We're particularly excited about supporting Pygame and Java Swing.","_key":"10894f9fefe50"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"f4a4ce8babae","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Game Jam","_key":"f4a4ce8babae0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"8f45f511176f","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We wanted to give you a reason to try out our new GUI capabilities, so we kicked off our very first ","_key":"8f45f511176f0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["b8981c67c9db"],"text":"game jam","_key":"8f45f511176f1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" on March 18th. It closes on April 18th, so there’s still plenty of time to show us what you can do. As for the winner? The grand prize is 1BTC ($4,031 at the time of writing).","_key":"8f45f511176f2"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"b8981c67c9db","_type":"link","href":"/jam"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"4c3b9f8ac81d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Technology","_key":"4c3b9f8ac81d0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"3916e9730a9f","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We like to release early and often. So while this works, and we're proud of what we've done, there's still a long way to go. Right now, we're piping the X Window system through VNC through WebSockets to your browser, which is not the most efficient way to do this — we have a lot of ideas on how we could improve it.","_key":"3916e9730a9f0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"e09ce595960a","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"To stay true to our ","_key":"e09ce595960a0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["3abfc30d73b0"],"text":"adaptive IDE","_key":"e09ce595960a1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" principle — the IDE should \"do the right thing\" when you need it — we use ","_key":"e09ce595960a2"},{"_type":"span","marks":["bd2e64d03c90"],"text":"LD_PRELOAD","_key":"e09ce595960a3"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" to figure out when an application is trying to open a window and then we start X in the background and reveal the screen in the environment. This has the effect of delighting our users:","_key":"e09ce595960a4"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"3abfc30d73b0","_type":"link","href":"/platform"},{"_key":"bd2e64d03c90","_type":"link","href":"stderr"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"3711caa2655d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Awesome! Plotting on ","_key":"3711caa2655d0"},{"_type":"span","marks":["deb4c18f09f6"],"text":"https://t.co/DcPy3gZFUO","_key":"3711caa2655d1"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" using GR and ","_key":"3711caa2655d2"},{"_type":"span","marks":["66422ad15e4d"],"text":"#JuliaLang","_key":"3711caa2655d3"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":". ","_key":"3711caa2655d4"},{"_type":"span","marks":["2e39927fe78f"],"text":"pic.twitter.com/K4GPBjOZgR","_key":"3711caa2655d5"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"\n\n— Josef Heinen (@josef_heinen) ","_key":"3711caa2655d6"},{"_type":"span","marks":["1a2dd0758c11"],"text":"March 9, 2019","_key":"3711caa2655d7"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"deb4c18f09f6","_type":"link","href":"https://t.co/DcPy3gZFUO"},{"_key":"66422ad15e4d","_type":"link","href":"https://twitter.com/hashtag/JuliaLang?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"},{"_key":"2e39927fe78f","_type":"link","href":"https://t.co/K4GPBjOZgR"},{"_key":"1a2dd0758c11","_type":"link","href":"https://twitter.com/josef_heinen/status/1104288994110644224?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"}],"_type":"block","style":"blockquote"},{"_key":"a600fd4c94f0","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Finally, depending on how far you are from our data center (US-central) you might feel a delay, which we're also working on making better by replicating our data center (watch out ","_key":"a600fd4c94f00"},{"_type":"span","marks":["53d441c7a71f"],"text":"Google Stadia","_key":"a600fd4c94f01"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":").","_key":"a600fd4c94f02"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"53d441c7a71f","_type":"link","href":"https://store.google.com/magazine/stadia"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"e6dc4d6b6634","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Please leave us ","_key":"e6dc4d6b66340"},{"_type":"span","marks":["86b6f631e992"],"text":"feedback","_key":"e6dc4d6b66341"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" so we can improve. Or come ","_key":"e6dc4d6b66342"},{"_type":"span","marks":["9f3b30dcd43b"],"text":"work with us","_key":"e6dc4d6b66343"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" so we can make it better together.","_key":"e6dc4d6b66344"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"86b6f631e992","_type":"link","href":"https://repl.it/feedback"},{"_key":"9f3b30dcd43b","_type":"link","href":"/jobs"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"0cffc3046f78","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Get started","_key":"0cffc3046f780"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"h2"},{"_key":"7f99e8a0ef54","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Early reception has been tremendous, and replers have been building amazing things. Take a look at some of the submissions in our ","_key":"7f99e8a0ef540"},{"_type":"span","marks":["34561f8df563"],"text":"game jam","_key":"7f99e8a0ef541"},{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" or give it a spin yourself:","_key":"7f99e8a0ef542"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"34561f8df563","_type":"link","href":"/talk/challenge"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"675319531427","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["3b1fb6972f45"],"text":"Start with Pygame","_key":"6753195314270"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"3b1fb6972f45","_type":"link","href":"/languages/pygame"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"195a436a2ad7","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["d0937eba022b"],"text":"Start with LOVE2D","_key":"195a436a2ad70"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"d0937eba022b","_type":"link","href":"/languages/love2d"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"f584a3145f0d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["6a042cc58864"],"text":"Start with Java Swing","_key":"f584a3145f0d0"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"6a042cc58864","_type":"link","href":"/languages/java_swing"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"27eca881ea61","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["4afa98970886"],"text":"Start with Python Tkinter","_key":"27eca881ea610"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"4afa98970886","_type":"link","href":"/languages/tkinter"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"272763eee3f3","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":["40b54ead3cd0"],"text":"Start with Pyxel","_key":"272763eee3f30"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"40b54ead3cd0","_type":"link","href":"/languages/pyxel"}],"_type":"block","style":"normal","level":1,"listItem":"bullet"},{"_key":"d439e08848e4","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"We're supporting these frameworks out of the box, but very soon, we'll roll this out to all of our languages. If you're impatient, then you can use our base image to Install (pkg-install) and run your framework.","_key":"d439e08848e40"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"},{"_key":"e31900c72d6d","children":[{"_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Happy game development!","_key":"e31900c72d6d0"}],"markDefs":[],"_type":"block","style":"normal"}],"publishedAt":"2019-03-21T04:02:18.184Z"}